{
  "name": "vigiapp",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "main": "expo-router/entry",
  "type": "commonjs",
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=20.19.4"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "start": "expo start",
    "android": "expo run:android",
    "ios": "expo run:ios",
    "web": "expo start --web",
    "lint": "expo lint",
    "reset-project": "node ./scripts/reset-project.js",
    "android:bare": "cd android && gradlew installDebug",

    // --- utilitaires demo “prehash-saltid-demo” SANS passer tout le projet en ESM ---
    "signup": "node --input-type=module -e \"import('./client/cryptoClient.js').then(async m=>{const r=await m.signup(process.env.API_ORIGIN||'http://localhost:3000','test@example.com','motdepasse'); console.log(r);})\"",
    "login": "node --input-type=module -e \"import('./client/loginAdapter.js').then(async m=>{const r=await m.login(process.env.API_ORIGIN||'http://localhost:3000','test@example.com','motdepasse'); console.log(r);})\"",
    "start:server": "node server/index.js",

    // --- tests ---
    "test": "jest --runInBand",
    "test:watch": "jest --watch"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@react-native-async-storage/async-storage": "2.1.2",

    "@react-native-firebase/app": "23.0.0",

    "dotenv": "^17.2.1"

    "@babel/core": "^7.25.2",
